commits.message: [Tests] Cleans up snapshot tests for Xcode 7.3.1.
[Podfile] Adds comment for specific pod commit.
[CI] Split up failing test + switch to syncrhonous testing.
[CI] Fixes intermittently failing test comparing dates.
[Deps] Updates dependencies to latest Swift 2.x versions.
[Feedback] Adds clarifying comments as per feedback in #609.

issue.title: Xcode updates
issue.body:
I don't want to spend much time on this project, but I do want to keep it up to date with current tools so that we can deploy any fixes quickly. 

I tried updating to CocoaPods 1.0, but things went quickly awry. It's a large job, but not necessary for now.
